90
00:05:27,460 --> 00:05:30,789
Throughout my life,
I never wanted what wasn't mine.

91
00:05:31,330 --> 00:05:34,229
I'm not ashamed to say
I lived an honest law-abiding life.

92
00:05:34,960 --> 00:05:37,099
My husband won't accept this,

93
00:05:37,570 --> 00:05:39,599
and it'll only harm Sang Ah's standing.

94
00:05:39,839 --> 00:05:42,070
So that no harm comes to Ms. Jin... No.

95
00:05:42,739 --> 00:05:45,710
I'll help cement her standing
and make it even stronger.

96
00:05:45,710 --> 00:05:46,710
No.

97
00:05:47,979 --> 00:05:49,109
Change your mind.

98
00:05:56,120 --> 00:05:58,890
(Grace Shim Beauty Studio)

99
00:05:58,890 --> 00:05:59,919
