doesn't get divorced twice.

104
00:06:13,299 --> 00:06:15,539
(Grace Shim Beauty Studio)

105
00:06:16,909 --> 00:06:19,179
My gosh. What did I tell you?

106
00:06:19,239 --> 00:06:20,940
I said something was up with them.

107
00:06:20,940 --> 00:06:23,549
I thought they were close
because they'd studied abroad together.

108
00:06:23,549 --> 00:06:25,080
How could she and Mr. Jeon...

109
00:06:25,409 --> 00:06:27,349
My heart's racing.

110
00:06:27,750 --> 00:06:30,450
Mine too. It's crazy.

111
00:06:31,520 --> 00:06:32,560
Hey.

112
00:06:33,620 --> 00:06:35,419
What do you think about this?

113
00:06:35,630 --> 00:06:38,830
- My friend invested in it. It folds.
- It's awesome.

114
00:06:39,229 --> 00:06:40,299
Isn't it nice?

115
00:06:40,529 --> 00:06:42,570
- Do you want one?
- I'd like that.

116
00:06:42,570 --> 00:06:43,770
Keep this one, then.

117
00:06:58,580 --> 00:07:01,320
I met her once because we do business.

118
00:07:01,580 --> 00:07:03,349
I knew she'd get into trouble one day.

119
00:07:03,690 --> 00:07:07,120
It was crazy from the start,
but I only got the last bit.

120
00:07:07,359 --> 00:07:09,690
I didn't edit it to make it look extreme.

121
00:07:09,890 --> 00:07:11,390
This is what really went down.

122
00:07:11,589 --> 00:07:13,760
It was much more fun to witness.

123
00:07:14,000 --> 00:07:16,299
Reality's crazier than TV.

124
00:07:17,070 --> 00:07:18,200
Darn it.

125
00:07:34,620 --> 00:07:36,219
I met with your mother today.

126
00:07:38,289 --> 00:07:40,190
She treated me like a cheater...

127
00:07:41,159 --> 00:07:43,289
who's ruining your perfectly fine life.

128
00:07:45,130 --> 00:07:46,500
It wasn't nice.

129
00:07:47,760 --> 00:07:48,830
What about me?

130
00:07:49,700 --> 00:07:52,640
Do you know what happened
because your mother barged in?

131
00:07:54,339 --> 00:07:56,440
- Take a look.
- Let's get the facts straight.

132
00:07:56,539 --> 00:07:59,179
Let me tell you their names.

133
