- You. Don't film us.
- What's this?

134
00:08:01,140 --> 00:08:02,909
Why am I in this video?

135
00:08:02,979 --> 00:08:04,750
- Shoot.
- It's the exact amount.

136
00:08:04,750 --> 00:08:06,380
- Gather and count the bills.
- She did this to vent...

137
00:08:06,380 --> 00:08:07,880
because she saw us with your mother.

138
00:08:08,320 --> 00:08:11,219
Your ex-wife is really something.

139
00:08:12,620 --> 00:08:13,620
