and stop it from spreading.

168
00:10:05,699 --> 00:10:08,600
Break up with Jeon, get him to resign,

169
00:10:08,740 --> 00:10:10,069
and call So Woo.

170
00:10:10,110 --> 00:10:12,039
No. I'll call him.

171
00:10:13,110 --> 00:10:16,449
