200
00:11:54,779 --> 00:11:56,779
I'm sure we'll find something
if we look hard enough.

201
00:11:57,779 --> 00:12:00,779
Whether it's a semi-basement
or on a roof, a three-room...

202
00:12:00,779 --> 00:12:04,449
Do develop rundown areas
and provide more housing,

203
