to prevent property speculation.

212
00:12:26,840 --> 00:12:29,110
As a result of this project,
Manjang-dong will become...

213
00:12:29,110 --> 00:12:32,579
a 5,000-household complex
worth investing in.

214
00:12:32,579 --> 00:12:33,750
Seon Ju.

215
00:12:35,679 --> 00:12:37,020
