216
00:12:41,890 --> 00:12:42,929
Are you having fun?

217
00:12:49,130 --> 00:12:50,230
(Extreme Measures to Provide Housing)

218
00:12:50,230 --> 00:12:51,230
(Manjang-dong Selected
for Development Project)

219
00:12:51,929 --> 00:12:54,439
Sir. There's great news
about the house you bought.

220
00:12:54,900 --> 00:12:56,510
You got really lucky.

221
00:13:00,610 --> 00:13:02,809
The Manjang-dong residents got a windfall.

222
00:13:03,380 --> 00:13:06,020
You could sell now and make
at least 100,000 to 200,000 dollars.

223
00:13:07,620 --> 00:13:10,220
Is the person who bought our house
a speculator?

224
00:13:11,419 --> 00:13:12,590
No.

225
00:13:13,789 --> 00:13:17,429
