we could take advantage of.

226
00:13:17,529 --> 00:13:19,360
This is driving me crazy.

227
00:13:22,900 --> 00:13:25,069
Let's go to the real estate agent...

228
00:13:25,069 --> 00:13:26,740
and see what he has to say.

229
00:13:26,970 --> 00:13:28,569
- Come with me.
- Okay.

230
00:13:32,840 --> 00:13:35,279
There had been some suspicious movement.

231
00:13:35,679 --> 00:13:39,850
