aren't made or announced...

237
00:13:51,929 --> 00:13:54,000
like they're a top-secret mission.

238
00:13:54,059 --> 00:13:56,569
What government policy
is announced so suddenly?

239
00:13:56,569 --> 00:13:59,069
Has this ever happened before?

240
00:13:59,069 --> 00:14:00,939
- No.
- That's right.

241
00:14:00,939 --> 00:14:05,370
